item.title: Swimming
item.description: General Swimming Tips :dolphin: Keep Body Horizontal Head Looking Straight Down Enter Stroke Extended, Angle Fingers Flat on the Surface Turn Body to Breathe High Elbow 4 Quick Kicks Per Stroke Keep Non-Pulling Arm Straight in Water until Other Arm almost Enters Workouts Here are some typical workout plans to get started: Warm up Rest Time 150m easy, 50m any @ 2:45 ~ 3:00 pace 30s Fill in Thursday Main Rest Time 300 easys Fill in Thursday Swimming Forms Freestyle (Frontcrawl) Fast.
